"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1933945-celine-dion-paris-olympics-next-move\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Celine Dionhas been revelling in a wave of enthusiasm for live performances following her triumphant Olympic stint in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 120, \"end\": 125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.862044199104664e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 56, the star enthralled an enormous audience at the base of the Eiffel Tower last month with a dazzling show for the Olympics' opening gala.\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Post that spectacular turn, buzz is that she's all geared up to delight her followers with more of her acclaimed vocal magic.\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The revelation comes on the heels of Dion's recent public announcement that she was grappling with Stiff Person Syndrome, a diagnosis that prompted her hiatus from the music scene in 2022.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Celine graced the occasion with Edith Piaf's iconic \\\"Hymne A L'Amour,\\\" and a confidant divulged to In Touch: \\\"She's determined to keep proving everyone wrong by performing again.\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"score\": 0.9999999912251951, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Edith Piaf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The success of this has only made her even more hungry to perform again.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's working on plans for her next performance.\\\"\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Battling Stiff Person Syndrome has not dampened Celine's resolve; indeed, sources say her return feels like a true miracle.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, it signals the beginning rather than the end of her journey to recovery.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A friend deeply involved in Celines career mentioned: \\\"It does not mean she's out of the woods or over this horrible disease, there is still a long road ahead.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will need to keep fighting every day towards her healing, but she's not giving up and intends to keep fighting and setting a positive example for her fans and for anyone battling this disease.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", reportsthe Mirror.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:BBC fans slam Olympics pundits after Men's 200m final - 'Stop making excuses'    Despite her stunning performance at the opening ceremony of the Paris 2024 Olympics, global superstar Celine Dion remained grounded.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9997807343094955, \"rank\": 0.0002167668248231184, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1666, \"end\": 1677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.66493580594843e-40, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just hours after the event, she was spotted taking a leisurely stroll around Paris, dressed casually in a denim hoodie and long-sleeved shirt.\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.862044199104664e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The singer was visibly moved when a fan presented her with a single rose.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Noah Lyles diagnosed with Covid minutes after leaving 200m track in a wheelchair  Do not miss:Bradly Sinden withdraws from taekwondo fight as Team GB miss out on bronze medal  Do not miss:Team GB star 'says horrible things' after missing out on Olympic medal  Contrary to earlier reports that Dion had received a staggering $2million for her Olympic appearance, it has been revealed that this was not the case.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1928, \"end\": 1938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999896740519, \"rank\": 1.0290846508362374e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to UNILAD, Olympic organisers confirmed that none of the artists were paid for their performances.\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2352, \"end\": 2358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UNILAD\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UNILAD\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UNILAD\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UNILAD\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Committee issued a statement saying: \\\"This commitment reflects their desire to participate in a historic event for France and for the world of sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2576, \"end\": 2582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9991934861096647, \"rank\": 0.0005110365719225047, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the weeks leading up to her first performance in two years, Dion opened up about her health struggles in an interview with Hoda Kotb.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2739, \"end\": 2748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoda Kotb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  She described her condition as feeling like \\\"It's like somebody is strangling you,\\\" demonstrating the physical sensations by pressing on her throat.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"It's like you are talking like that, and you cannot go higher or lower.\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It gets into a spasm.\\\"\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3390, \"end\": 3403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0153049767236198e-25, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3439, \"end\": 3452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0153049767236198e-25, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"